461
00:36:57,760 --> 00:37:00,080
-Vamos conversar, Alfie.
-Conversar?

462
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:03,760
Tudo bem, vamos conversar.

463
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:07,840
